objectives.name: Primary Efficacy Objective
objectives.text: To evaluate the efficacy of BIVV001 weekly prophylaxis as estimated by the mean ABR and one-sided 97.5% CI in Arm A.

objectives.name: Key Secondary Efficacy Objective
objectives.text: To perform an intra-patient comparison of ABR during the BIVV001 weekly prophylaxis treatment period versus the historical prophylaxis ABR

objectives.name: Secondary Patient Reported Outcomes Objective
objectives.text: To evaluate the effect of BIVV001 on physical health, pain intensity, and joint health

objectives.name: Safety Objective
objectives.text: To assess the safety and immunogenicity of IV BIVV001

objectives.name: Pharmacokinetics Objective
objectives.text: To assess the pharmacokinetics of IV BIVV001

objectives.name: Exploratory Objective
objectives.text: To evaluate participants’ expectations of treatment and perception of treatment impact

endpoints.name: Primary Efficacy Endpoint
endpoints.text: Annualized Bleeding Rate (ABR) in Arm A

endpoints.name: Key Secondary Efficacy Endpoint
endpoints.text: Intra-patient comparison of ABR during the BIVV001 weekly prophylaxis treatment period versus the historical prophylaxis ABR

endpoints.name: Haem-A-QoL Physical Health Score
endpoints.text: Change from baseline to Week 52 in Haem-A-QoL (≥17 years old) Physical Health score

endpoints.name: PROMIS Pain Intensity 3a
endpoints.text: Change from baseline to Week 52 in PROMIS Pain Intensity 3a

endpoints.name: HJHS Total Score
endpoints.text: Change from baseline to Week 52 in Hemophilia Joint Health Score (HJHS) total score

endpoints.name: Safety Endpoints
endpoints.text: Incidence and severity of AEs, clinically significant changes in laboratory parameters, vital signs, and physical examination findings

endpoints.name: PK Parameters
endpoints.text: PK parameters summarized for both the one-stage aPTT clotting assay and two-stage chromogenic assay

endpoints.name: Exit Interview Endpoint
endpoints.text: Participants’ expectations of treatment and perception of treatment impact assessed via exit interview

estimands.name: Primary Efficacy Estimand - ABR in Arm A
estimands.populationSummary: Previously treated patients (PTPs) ≥12 years of age with severe hemophilia A (ITT/Full Analysis Set) Summary measure: Mean ABR estimated via Negative-Binomial regression with one-sided 97.5% CI.

intercurrentEvents.name: Treatment discontinuation
intercurrentEvents.text: Participant permanently discontinues study treatment before 52 weeks

intercurrentEvents.name: Use of non-study FVIII products
intercurrentEvents.text: Use of FVIII products other than BIVV001 (except in life-threatening emergencies)

estimands.analysisPopulation: Previously treated patients (PTPs) ≥12 years of age with severe hemophilia A (ITT/Full Analysis Set)
estimands.summaryMeasure: Mean ABR estimated via Negative-Binomial regression with one-sided 97.5% CI

estimands.name: Key Secondary Efficacy Estimand - Intra-patient ABR Comparison
estimands.populationSummary: Participants in Arm A with ≥6 months study duration and ≥6 months historical prophylaxis data Summary measure: Median difference in ABR (Non-inferiority margin of 4).

intercurrentEvents.name: Study withdrawal
intercurrentEvents.text: Participant withdraws from study before completing 6 months of BIVV001 treatment

estimands.treatment: BIVV001 50 IU/kg IV QW vs. Historical FVIII Prophylaxis
estimands.analysisPopulation: Participants in Arm A with ≥6 months study duration and ≥6 months historical prophylaxis data
estimands.summaryMeasure: Median difference in ABR (Non-inferiority margin of 4)

estimands.name: Secondary Efficacy Estimand - Physical Health Score
estimands.populationSummary: Adult patients (≥17 years old) in Arm A Summary measure: Adjusted mean change from baseline using MMRM.

intercurrentEvents.name: Treatment discontinuation
intercurrentEvents.text: Discontinuation of BIVV001 prior to Week 52 assessment

estimands.analysisPopulation: Adult patients (≥17 years old) in Arm A
estimands.variableOfInterest: Change from baseline to Week 52 in Haem-A-QoL Physical Health score
estimands.summaryMeasure: Adjusted mean change from baseline using MMRM

estimands.name: Secondary Efficacy Estimand - Pain Intensity
estimands.populationSummary: Participants in Arm A Summary measure: Adjusted mean change from baseline using MMRM.

intercurrentEvents.name: Treatment discontinuation
intercurrentEvents.text: Discontinuation of BIVV001 prior to Week 52 assessment

estimands.variableOfInterest: Change from baseline to Week 52 in PROMIS Pain Intensity 3a
estimands.summaryMeasure: Adjusted mean change from baseline using MMRM

estimands.populationSummary: Participants in Arm A Summary measure: Adjusted mean change from baseline using MMRM.

intercurrentEvents.name: Treatment discontinuation
intercurrentEvents.text: Discontinuation of BIVV001 prior to Week 52 assessment
